Template: kernel-chooser/which-kernel
Type: select
Choices: ${kernels}
_Description: Select which kernel to install into /target/
 These are the kernels available from the APT sources.  One of them
 need to be installed to be able to boot the system from hard drive.

Template: kernel-chooser/no-kernels-found
Type: note
_Description: No installable kernel was found in the APT sources defined
 This is rather strange, and probably fatal.  You will have to continue
 as best as you can.  Good luck.
